{"tid":418701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【平反六四】安永海外併購合伙人張曉青參與過64？","createTime":"2017-09-29T18:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T18:12:33.000Z","uid":124991,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee340118b7b87cbbcd386a22637d1679da844cb7","tid":418701,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T18:58:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dragrnovlayins/status/912970789187702785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdragrnovlayins%2Fstatus%2F912970789187702785&d=%2FzwbaqiJ72DmMrrXVyJ09QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=156d5e6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdragrnovlayins%2Fstatus%2F912970789187702785&h=36567e2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dragrnovlayins/status/912970789187702785</a><br />\n到了兌現推友們的承諾的時候了。<br />\n張曉青（Shau Zhang），美國公民，安永（EY）海外併購合夥人。完成多宗海航併購交易，包括目前正在調查的瑞士瑞士港項目和cassa酒店項目。<br />\n此人當年是CSPA1992拿到綠卡的並且曾多次炫耀：公主習明澤在安永的實習是她安排的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dragrnovlayins/status/912972088213934080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdragrnovlayins%2Fstatus%2F912972088213934080&d=%2FzwbaqiJ72DmMrrXVyJ09QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=0d977065\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdragrnovlayins%2Fstatus%2F912972088213934080&h=fd1fe81c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dragrnovlayins/status/912972088213934080</a><br />\n所謂CSPA1992，也就是大家常說的六四綠卡。也就是說，張女士是典型的拿著美國對留學生的庇護之後，又和中共貪腐集團勾結。<br />\n張曉青加入安永20年，並借助和中共高層的關係，成為麻州波士頓的華人僑領，到華人留學生所在的學校四處活動，拉起協助盜國賊轉移財產的團隊。海航境外基本被安永壟斷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知道？"},{"pid":"72ffa6d878bda72fded3495a6c8dcf5ad8632666","tid":418701,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T19:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc49edd5d8811c6743c9f89a93764371d5678c3","tid":418701,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T20:08:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e8cc052c713ac968922a9b430dc6c0fa5952513","tid":418701,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:20:42.000Z","msg":"咁即係海航係習總有份？"},{"pid":"42600fd67798b9930442ac182feb347ae7a79f76","tid":418701,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:21:31.000Z","msg":"定六四其實都係維尼有份幕後搞？"},{"pid":"404c89d39f99070fd4fc7525791107a1e1f40e6b","tid":418701,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:23:38.000Z","msg":"超, 689夠遣責過64屠城啦"},{"pid":"5bd4ff60d6bbeb3dc09391e0d8c1f35998afa763","tid":418701,"uid":1082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"姐係當年中共有人扮六四青年，並籍此定居美國，可能仲有間諜添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5b5ed3eb51e385942305cf8679afe3d298135c","tid":418701,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>定六四其實都係維尼有份幕後搞？</blockquote><br />\n邊關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我係想知張女士係參與過64定係扮參與64<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c47bef8ca643a5c273b1ef7a1fa791c2496e17d","tid":418701,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/dragrnovlayins/status/912970789187702785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdragrnovlayins%2Fstatus%2F912970789187702785&d=%2FzwbaqiJ72