ime":"2017-09-30T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐係當年中共有人扮六四青年，並籍此定居美國，可能仲有間諜添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n錯<br />\n係支共既間諜參與64<br />\n衰左之後走去外國做支共既間諜"},{"pid":"ac4d3a933b34810f207473c6b708e725d064aadb","tid":418701,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超, 689夠遣責過64屠城啦</blockquote><br />\n據聞當年好多人係扮支持64，所以之後先會出現「忽然愛國」風潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6792624c0ec2ed76d84af7b5e62fbc61a5ab47e7","tid":418701,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>姐係當年中共有人扮六四青年，並籍此定居美國，可能仲有間諜添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n錯<br />\n係支共既間諜參與64<br />\n衰左之後走去外國做支共既間諜</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acb18c04d9da314356e119f32112905b0d70fc8","tid":418701,"uid":81052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_Student_Protection_Act_of_1992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FChinese_Student_Protection_Act_of_1992&d=%2FzwbaqiJ72DmMrrXVyJ09QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4f23f19d\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_Student_Protection_Act_of_1992</a>"},{"pid":"be3c5325afdf46723d78aea11fd0c12dff0be132","tid":418701,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_Student_Protection_Act_of_1992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FChinese_Student_Protection_Act_of_1992&d=%2FzwbaqiJ72DmMrrXVyJ09QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4f23f19d\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_Student_Protection_Act_of_1992</a></blockquote><br />\nThe Executive Director of Asia Watch, a large human-rights organization presence in China, spoke out against the CSPA, calling it unnecessary. According to the Executive Director, the only students that may have needed protection from their native country would be those that participated in televised or advertised speeches and those who wrote articles.<br />\n<br />\nA document from the U.S. Immigration and Naturalization noted, &ldquo;According to a cable from the U.S. Consul in Shanghai, China, over 120 returning [students]&hellip; who had come to China for various reasons were interviewed [as they prepared to go back to the U.S.]. Not one of them reported a problem.&rdquo; These students that returned home for a visit during the time that this Act was in effect were still eligible to apply for green cards.<br />\n<br />\n講得有道理，好多都係unnecessary ，背後係咪涉及利益輸送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236f90e1c79bceca69e3d96e882df99f3110a1c2","tid":418701,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"照咁睇，「中國自由派」同「溫和穆斯林」係咪冇大分別？泛民點睇？"},{"pid":"109dff19f535554cc114e8be35920c37029eeec5","tid":418701,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:59:53.000Z","msg":"即係想表達乜？"},{"pid":"c8a2dba4a8024642603dd26fd8b102f4590999f8","tid":418701,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照咁睇，「中國自由派」同「溫和穆斯林」係咪冇大分別？泛民點睇？</blockquote><br />\n無咩大分別<br />\n班民運人士就爽聲反台獨既<br />\n咁你望下泛民對台獨港獨既態度咪知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\